divs: sighting detailsusing my 8" schmidt\cass celestron telescope with a ccd camera linked with my laptop i caught this event while setting up my system. event occurred at 42 seconds into the video. i caught it while watching the process on my laptop. immediately looked into the sky but could not see any evidence of a plane or lights of a plane. observing conditions were light cloud cover which was spotty, cool evening temperature approx. 61 degrees.
